# UI Guardrails

- Do not introduce new frontend frameworks for the UI.
- Do not use React, Angular, or Vue unless explicitly requested.
- Do not mix SPA patterns with server-side rendering in the same feature.
- Prefer the existing server-rendered stack: Thymeleaf, HTMX, and Tailwind.

```text
Preferred stack: Thymeleaf + HTMX + Tailwind
Avoid: React, Angular, Vue, or hybrid SPA/server-rendered flows
```
